abstract: Jhonattan Vegas and Brian Stuard share third-round lead at Zurich Classic golf tournament; other golf news noted.

headline.print_headline: Golf; Two Share Lead in Louisiana

snippet: Jhonattan Vegas birdied two holes in the rain-delayed third round of the Zurich Classic in Avondale, La., giving him a share of the lead with Brian Stuard.
lead_paragraph: Jhonattan Vegas birdied two holes in the rain-delayed third round of the Zurich Classic in Avondale, La., giving him a share of the lead with Brian Stuard.
